'''雷蒙·A·拉米雷斯'''（{{lang-es|'''Ramón A. Ramírez'''}}，{{bd|1982年|9月16日|||Ramírez, Ramón}}），出生于[[卡瓜|卡瓜]]，[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]棒球运动员，是效力于[[美国职棒大联盟|美国职棒大联盟]][[波士顿红袜|波士顿红袜]]的[[投手|投手]]。他{{MLBy|2004年}}和[[辛辛那提红人|辛辛那提红人]]签约，并在{{MLBy|2008年}}8月30日首次登上大联盟。{{MLBy|2009年}}赛季结束后被[[坦帕湾光芒|坦帕湾光芒]]签下<ref>{{cite web | title = Rays release right-hander Ramirez | url = http://tampabay.rays.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091203&content_id=7749356&vkey=news_tb&fext=.jsp&c_id=tb | date = 2009-12-03 | accessdate = 2010-01-25 | author = Bill Chastain | publisher = [[MLB.com|MLB.com]] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120310052417/http://tampabay.rays.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091203&content_id=7749356&vkey=news_tb&fext=.jsp&c_id=tb | archivedate = 2012-03-10 }}</ref>，但随后即被球队释出，12月9日又被[[波士顿红袜|波士顿红袜]]签下<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=301690 | title = RED SOX SIGN ANOTHER RAMON RAMIREZ | date = 2009-12-09 | accessdate = 2010-01-25 | archive-date = 2009-12-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091211064738/http://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=301690 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

